    <string name="gallery_import_header">Import: photos · animations · video</string>
    <string name="gallery_import_subtitle">Pick from your gallery via the Android Photo Picker; each file is encrypted with your master key, given a 384px thumbnail, and saved to the vault below. Originals on the device are NOT removed yet — that needs explicit confirmation and is coming in the next step.</string>
    <string name="gallery_import_supported">Accepted: JPEG, PNG, HEIC/HEIF, WEBP, AVIF, GIF, BMP / MP4, MKV, WebM, 3GP. Files in other formats that appear in the picker are rejected at import to keep the parser surface small.</string>

